{"tid":2083201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張可森：請香港人全面拒絕CCTVB任何訪問","createTime":"2020-06-28T14:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T15:32:11.000Z","uid":153600,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a5d32778d525e303dc6ad0d571cd6443db0767","tid":2083201,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"請各位香港人，全面拒絕TVB任何訪問。<br />\n<br />\n剛才我係博愛醫院，跟進剛才嘅 #朗屏白衣人襲擊案。然後有TVB記者到場意圖採訪，街坊已經講唔想接受，後來先表示可以訪問，但係 #唔可以出樣。<br />\n<br />\n點知，過咗一陣，我竟然見到有人set機，想係玻璃窗外面偷拍街坊，我立即上前喝止，記者仲回覆話：「淨係想影小朋友側面啫。」<br />\n<br />\n講明 #唔出樣就係唔出樣，但係該名TVB記者仲係唔停機，直至我以身擋住鏡頭，先一面唔憤氣咁收機。<br />\n<br />\n無線新聞你不如改名 #無恥新聞 啦，當事人講明唔可以出樣，仲要冇問過同意之下偷拍，已經唔係冇職業操守咁簡單，根本就係無恥。<br />\n<br />\n區議員嘅天職就係要 #保護街坊，我唔會容許任何人去騷擾我街坊，但係有某啲記者，就係為咗跑新聞，罔顧當事人嘅感受，去到醫院騷擾當事人，我過去見過太多次，所以剛才先去醫院，保護街坊。<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多街坊，會一時心軟接受TVB訪問。但我希望大家記得TVB係點樣無恥咁刪改新聞，無論前線記者有幾可憐，都唔好唔記得佢哋係為一間無良嘅公司打工。<br />\n<br />\n本人以後唔會再接受TVB任何訪問，亦都希望各位香港人一齊抵制TVB。"},{"pid":"fee74135259d5400197267234b855331a9c61068","tid":2083201,"uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"所以抵制CCTVB廣告商嘅活動一定要繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad81e5c366d96bd2718ffeed0e90991b6313989c","tid":2083201,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"source <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d635ea495ec985e63c4a67d2240903c0bc721d1e","tid":2083201,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be16b677080d187d7ae54d8d443723efc433a3ac","tid":2083201,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad81e5c366d96bd2718ffeed0e90991b6313989c","tid":2083201,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"source <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"張可森fb"},{"pid":"8a82777fc094587a427d2e3bc7204d2ab368bb5d","tid":2083201,"uid":40520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"前線係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa0106549ea150064c89231e01ad21468eb87ed","tid":2083201,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"Tvb 罪大惡極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b55835fce036e99f4d3d66e53cd3a3f744d997b","tid":2083201,"uid":34612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4942db2f3a3efb5bf949b3abfcb1056b10b9ee3","tid":2083201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cc9e75cd9478c4ca7a1b9c8612dac9d8b3feefc","tid":2083201,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"唔好信唔影樣 呢樣野<br />\ntbb 更不了"},{"pid":"8592053818fb80ce56d0761660aaf46172a77934","tid":2083201,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"103660022afdce989b568ab90ec3285d12cfb042","tid":2083201,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f7d85be18e6f5b2923cabe836d0be5d9fdf1083f","tid":2083201,"uid":264245,"like"